reviews.review_text: I was @ that show. What an amazing show.  The only time I went to the "Gahden."  Jerry broke a string during one of the 1st few tunes...Jack Straw was a beautiful opener...Iko Iko shook the balconies...Rain encore described the weather that day.  I'll never forget that show.
